Django Chat Application
This project is a simple chat application built with Django, a high-level Python web framework. 
It allows users to join chat rooms and exchange messages in real-time. This project demonstrates fundamental Django functionalities, 
including URL routing, models, views, and templates. It also incorporates AJAX for real-time updates without requiring page refreshes.

Features:
User Authentication: Secure user login and registration system.
Real-Time Messaging: Uses AJAX to update messages in real-time.
Multiple Chat Rooms: Users can create and join different chat rooms.
User-Friendly Interface: Clean and responsive UI for an enhanced user experience.
CSRF Protection: Secure against Cross-Site Request Forgery attacks.
SQLite Database: Uses SQLite for lightweight and easy-to-setup database management.
Technologies Used:
Frontend: HTML, CSS, JavaScript, jQuery
Backend: Django, Python
Database: SQLite
Version Control: Git, GitHub
